title: Location, Community, Quality Living. It Starts Here at The Well!

posting_body: ['Call Now -', 'show contact info', 'x 67', 'OR Text', '67', 'to', 'show contact info', 'to text our team directly.', 'This is a 1 Bedroom, 1 Bath, approximately 642 Sq.', 'Ft.', 'Welcome to The Well, a brand new apartment community in Henderson, Nevada, tailored to fit your ideal lifestyle.', 'LIVE WELL with thoughtful details such as quartz counters and large windows to let in the warm Nevada sunlight.', 'Enjoy the convenience of smart home features, such as activity notifications and lighting automation.', 'PLAY', 'WELL by the pool, at the fitness center or in the lounge.', "BE WELL in the heart of Union Village, the world's first integrated health village.", 'Anchored by Henderson Hospital, plans for Union Village include premium outdoor shopping, dining and entertainment venues, hotels, fitness clubs and more.', 'Call to schedule a tour today!', 'Features:', 'Spacious Studio, One-, Two- & Three-Bedroom Floor Plans, CASPAR Smart Home Technology, Walk-In Closets, Glass Tile Kitchen Backsplashes, Quartz Countertops, Choice of Two Stylish Interior Packages, Private Patios & Balconies*, Wood-Style Plank Flooring, Modern, Flat-Panel Cabinets with Under-Cabinet Lighting, WiFi Ready with Modem &', '1st Month', 'Free, Provided by Cox, GE Stainless Steel Appliances, Washers & Dryers', '* Only available in select apartments', '**Amenities may vary and are subject to change at any time.', 'Community Amenities:', 'Coffee Bar with TopBrewer App-Powered Espresso Machine, Sport Court & Playground, Question Mark-Shaped Pool with Spa Deck, Game Room with Billiards, Conference Room, Entertainment Kitchen with a Community Dining Space, Chic Clubhouse with a Fireplace & Big-Screen TVs, 24-Hour Fitness Center, Outdoor Lounge with BBQ Grills, 24/7 On-Demand Parcel Lockers', 'Pet Policy', 'Pets - allowed', 'Follow This Link for More Information:', '<URL>', 'kL4U3QKlz']
